3. Windows Vs Linux Comparision



Windows Vs Linux

Windows                                                           Linux

It is a proprietary software everything need to buy               It is an open source software everything is free
Less Secure                                                       More Secure
More costly                                                       Less Cost compare to windows
Chance to get a carpal tunnel syndrome                            There is no chance to get carpal tunnel syndrome
Developed by Microsoft corporation                                Developed by Linus Torvalds
Options need to select                                            You can develop anything as per your requirement
Kernel is not editable                                            Kernel is editable
